  Some cleanups.  Tidy ebuild.  Move all patches to ${FILESDIR}/${PV/.
  Remove old patches.

  Add patches to fix warnings with gcc-3.2:

    http://archive.linuxfromscratch.org/mail-archives/lfs-dev/2002/08/0228.html

